data.title: Debbie Harry of Blondie; Los Angeles punk legends X
data.meta_description: This week on Teenage Kicks, we celebrate the great Debbie Harry of Blondie — who's got a big birthday coming up on Monday. With her music, fashion, art and life, Debbie Harry has impacted generations — we'll pay tribute with some of her iconic songs this week on Teenage Kicks. We'll also profile the band X, who are taking the stage Saturday afternoon at Rock the Garden. A little pre-show punk rock with X, and Blondie, this week for Teenage Kicks.
data.text:
This week on Teenage Kicks, we celebrate the great Debbie Harry of Blondie — who's got a big birthday coming up on Monday. With her music, fashion, art and life, Debbie Harry has impacted generations — we'll pay tribute with some of her iconic songs this week on Teenage Kicks. We'll also profile the band X, who are taking the stage Saturday afternoon at Rock the Garden. A little pre-show punk rock with X, and Blondie, this week for Teenage Kicks.
